/*:
 * @plugindesc v1.0 Building System
 * @author ToshAngel
 * @target MZ
 * @version v1.0
 * @url https://toshaangel.itch.io
 * 
 * @param BuildingCategories
 * @text Building Categories
 * @type struct<BuildingCategory>[]
 * @default []
 * 
 * @param BuildingTypes
 * @text Building Types
 * @type struct<BuildingType>[]
 * @default []
 *  
 * @help
 * =============================================================================
 * ToshA Building System
 * =============================================================================
 * 
 * Description:
 * This plugin adds a building system to the game. It allows you
 * to place buildings on the map, manage their state, and interact
 * with other systems.
 * 
 * Main features:
 * - Placing buildings on the map
 * - Free positioning or grid snapping
 * - Building categories
 * - Appearance variants for each building
 * - Building state management (activation/deactivation)
 * - Information window with building parameters
 * - Resource consumption and production system
 * 
 * Integration with other plugins:
 * 1. ToshA_ResourceSystem.js
 *    - Required for resource management
 *    - Allows buildings to consume and produce resources
 * 
 * 2. ToshA_DynamicWeatherTime.js
 *    - Adds support for time of day and weather
 *    - Required for time-based resource production/consumption
 * 
 * 3. ToshA_FogOfWar.js (optional)
 *    - Adds fog of war support
 *    - Buildings can reveal visibility areas
 *    - Option to build only in visible areas
 * 
 * How to use:
 * 1. Controls:
 *    - B - building mode
 *    - V - building management mode
 *    - R - rotate building
 *    - ESC - exit mode
 *    - E - open building storage
 *    - Arrow keys - select category/variant
 * 
 * 2. Placing buildings:
 *    - Enter building mode
 *    - Select category and building
 *    - Place building on the map
 *    - Buildings can be placed freely or snapped to grid
 * 
 * 3. Managing buildings:
 *    - Enter management mode
 *    - Click on a building to view information
 *    - Buildings can be activated/deactivated
 *    - Buildings can be deleted
 * 
 * 4. Resources:
 *    - Buildings may require resources to build
 *    - Can produce resources over time
 *    - Can consume resources to function
 *    - When a building is deleted, some resources are returned
 * 
Notes:
- To enable building on a map, you MUST add map notes with allowed
  building categories using the format:
  <category(Category Name)>
  Building will be disabled on maps without these notes
- All building images should be in the img/buildings/ folder
- ToshA_ResourceSystem.js is required for resource functionality
- ToshA_DynamicWeatherTime.js is needed for time-based production
- The plugin can work with the ToshA_FogOfWar.js fog of war system
 * 
 * =============================================================================
 */

